<section xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>15-301</num>
  <heading>Definition and applicability.</heading>
  <text>As used in sections 15-302  , 15-303  , 15-305   to 15-307  , 15-309  , 15-317  , and 15-318  , “judgment” includes an unconditional decree for the payment of money, and sections 15-302   to 15-318   are applicable to such a decree.</text>
